    <note>Weng(1) Ji(2) [22307] CBD identifies him as a Fuqing county jinshi in 1082, but both Fujian TZ, 147.31a and Sanshan zhi record his degree in this year as facilitated. However, he is still active in early 12th century. His grandson, Hua [22308], is identified as a Chongan county resident and Ji(2) has the same generational name as Ji [22301] and Chun [22302], and chronological logic would also support an identification as a cousin of these two 1030 Chongan county jinshi. CBD, 3, 1977.</note>
